sentence: deacon oscar c. holloway| deacon oscar c. holloway age 89, of port st.
passed away quietly on monday, june 6, 2015 at treasure coast hospice following an extended illness.
deacon holloway was a longtime residence of port st.
lucie. he labored as a gardener for several years privately.
he was a faithful member of mount calvary missionary baptist church serving as deacon.
he leaves to mourn his passing his son, o. c. holloway, of ga.
three brothers, two sisters and four grandchildren, and a host of many sorrowing relatives and friends.
homegoing services will be held saturday, june 13, 2015 at 1:00 p. m. at mount calvary missionary baptist church, 904 bayou ave.
stuart, fl. with reverend elka harris, pastor.
friends may call on friday, june 12, 2015 from 5 - 7 p. m. at the church mentioned above.
